performance of motor skills. Although the specific definition of this concept is difficult to identify, there is\u8239 ?general agreement that }
{\fs18 the definition of the term }{\fs18 \ldblquote }{\fs18 attention,}{\fs18 \rdblquote }{\fs18  as we use it in this book,}{\fs18
 refers to }{\fs18 both}{\fs18  our limited \u173 ?capability to engage in multiple cognitive and motor activities simultaneously (commonly referred to as }
