information (e.g., Broadbent, 1958}{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-1 ; }{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-1 Welford, 1952, 1967), whereas others argued that it occurred later, after information was perceived or after it had been processed cognitively (e.g., Norman, 1968).\par }
