{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0 influential alternative proposed that information-}{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0 \line }{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0 processing functions could be carried out in parallel rather than serially, but attention limits were the result of the }
{\*\cs65\fs20\b0\i\expnd0\expndtw0 limited availability of resources}{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0  needed to carry out those functions. Just as you have limited economic resources to pay for your activities, we all have limited }
{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0 attentional}{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0  resources to do all the activities that we may attempt at one time.\par }
