\u8194\'20}{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw0 Vickers (1996) reported an experiment in which she recorded the eye movements of elite Canadian women basketball players as they prepared to shoot, and then shot, free throws. Two results are especially noteworthy. First, the \ldblquote experts\rdblquote  (they had made an average of }
