{\*\cs78\fs16\b\i\expnd0\expndtw0\cf1\outl0 Internal focus:}{\fs16  \ldblquote When you are attempting to jump as far as possible, I want you to focus your attention on extending your knees as rapidly as possible.\rdblquote \par }
